{"tid":1068753,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世]今年DSE考生請入","createTime":"2019-03-19T12:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T16:48:35.000Z","uid":6122,"like":6,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1f930110a2f5603aa1f98f2f62b1ff4b4ee86ede","tid":1068753,"uid":6122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:34:17.000Z","msg":"利伸過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家千祈唔好揀中大：<br />\n<br />\n首先，學術排名節節下跌，為做學術入中大已經過時，大部分人亦係玩多過返學，欠缺學習氣氛，唔少科目竟然用廣東話上堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，Canteen質素每況愈下，越嚟越貴，新龐can嘅價錢同氣氛完全唔適合坐滿全場，而且食完飯快快趣上堂嘅大學生根本冇時間享受個裝修；唔少canteen亦俾遊客侵佔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再者，中大嘅教學地點上至新亞逸夫，下至ELB嶺南場，返學已經要額外三個字等/搭校巴，有宿都唔例外，香港嘅大學大部分5分鐘內已經轉到堂，中大快則5分鐘，慢則半個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，中大校方幫外人多過幫自己人，外人霸晒校巴位講咗十年都未處理到，而家canteen俾遊客谷爆晒都係冇人處理，學生喺文化廣場掛banner就即刻有保安組出嚟搞，大部分學系嘅office職員亦經常當自己係老師咁鬧學生，唔講以為殺咗人老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a934fd8cdfc4fb32f7d9dbbe56f3267018740115","tid":1068753,"uid":167330,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:37:20.000Z","msg":"支持，香港只有一大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa660e5ef3caf6df6bf3d267a931076aef1b9573","tid":1068753,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n讀ive，人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d110169fbe2c0575dcc348ff90f1bbeaba814670","tid":1068753,"uid":95637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"應該入禾含"},{"pid":"acd319f04107a3edee4e5966b95e621eddd